title: #92Noon! Jordan Reid/Jensen Lewis/Pete Bercich/Pat Micheletti/Lavelle E Neal III/Chris Finch
description: --PA has guests front to back, Jordan Reid talks the impending NFL Draft, Jensen Lewis talks Twins and Indians later today, Pete Bercich checks in to talk all things purple, Pat Micheletti talks the playoff bound Wild, Lavelle E Neal III talks Twins, Gambling, and breaking a gumball machine, and Wolves coach Chris Finch talks his matchup with the Jazz tonight.
